{
  "id": "adv_main_01_05_06",
  "title": "星見編1章27話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_park-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこんな時間に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’re you doing here this late?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.021950113773346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 3.9582766175270114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ちょっと眠れなくて……\n{user}さんこそ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was having a hard time sleeping.\nWhat about you‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.991609950860342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……俺も、寝付けなくてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I couldn’t sleep either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.591609950860342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 12.220884319146437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それ、眠気覚ましの栄養剤ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But isn’t that an energy drink you’ve got there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.220884319146476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ no… You see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.13444447120031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 19.534444471200313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの……昼のことだけど……デートなんか\n本当にしてないんだ。あれは芽衣の冗談で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know… about this afternoon‚ I really didn’t go\non a date with Mei. She was just messing around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.667777804533642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなの、分かってます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guessed as much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.401111137866977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 27.401111137867
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 30.83444447120031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、渚に言われました。自分達が知らないものに\nもう少し目を向けてみようって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ Nagisa told me we should focus more\non what we don’t understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1344444712003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃないと、成長出来ないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Otherwise‚ we’ll never grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.96777780453363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 42.10111113786699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私、どうしても自分の分からないものを\n拒否してしまう所があるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a tendency to reject things\nI don’t understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.20111113786695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 47.60111113786695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それで\n{user}さんは何してたんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚\nwhat were you doing here‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.834444471200285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃんのデビューステージ、ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is where my sister had her debut live‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.30111113786695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ\nもしかして琴乃も――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nIs that why Kotono came here as well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.584444566567704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 58.55111123323437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "はい\nお姉ちゃん、どんな気持ちだったんだろうって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nI was thinking about how she must’ve felt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.88444456656769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 63.91777789990102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も見ていたのか？\n麻奈のデビューライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you were here then.\nYou saw Mana’s debut live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.98444456656765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 67.75111123323431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "私は…………後で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… watched it after.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.75111123323431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 70.4511112332343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "その頃は、お姉ちゃんを芸能界に取られるみたいで\n反対していましたから。アイドルになるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I hated show business\nbecause I felt like it was taking my sister from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.71777789990095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても見に来てほしいって言われて\n最後は直接部屋で頭まで下げられて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She really wanted me to watch her debut.\nShe even came to my room and begged me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.71777789990097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 84.88444456656764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "……私……なんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why… didn’t I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.88444456656764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（行かなかったんだろう……）\n（言葉は続かず、わずかに鼻をすする音が聞こえる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…so she didn't choose to go.）\n（Kotono’s words trail off‚ and I hear her quietly sniffling.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.89659874836597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 95.08266569375985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "実はみんなのデビューライブ\nここでやろうと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m thinking of using this place\nfor your debut live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.44933236042654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 99.24933236042654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.24933236042654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 100.18266569375982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのスタートは、ここがいいと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a good place for all of you to start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.18266569375982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 103.7482439160346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "……私、{user}さんが\nマネージャーで良かったのかもって、最近、思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ I’ve been thinking about\nhow lucky we are to have you as our manager‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.98157724936792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_06-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "最初、あんな嫌なことばかり言って\nすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry for all the nasty things\nSorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.51491058270132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-1d",
      "startTime": 116.34824391603463
    },
